<section class="masthead">
  <div class="badge"><span class="status-dot"></span>v1.0.4 Now Available</div>
  <h1 class="title">每款编辑器的<span>完整 .NET 开发</span>体验</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    一款开源语言服务器，提供完整的 C# 和 F# 智能体验——代码补全、诊断、重构、NuGet 管理、性能分析和调试——支持 VS Code、Neovim、Helix、Emacs、Zed 及所有兼容 LSP 的编辑器。无专有锁定，无需许可证。
  </p>
  <div class="button-row">
    <a class="button button-primary" href="/zh/docs/">快速入门</a>
    <a class="button button-secondary" href="https://github.com/MelbourneDeveloper/forge">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">code</span>
      查看 GitHub
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="panel">
  <div class="card-grid card-grid-three">
    <article class="metric-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined card-icon" aria-hidden="true">bolt</span>
      <h2>&lt;3s</h2>
      <p>冷启动时间</p>
    </article>
    <article class="metric-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined card-icon" aria-hidden="true">speed</span>
      <h2>&lt;100ms</h2>
      <p>代码补全 p50</p>
    </article>
    <article class="metric-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined card-icon" aria-hidden="true">extension_off</span>
      <h2>0</h2>
      <p>专有依赖</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="copy-block">
    <h2>任意编辑器，同一工具链</h2>
    <p>安装一次 Forge，即可在您喜欢的任何编辑器中获得完整的 .NET 开发体验——C# 和 F# 同等支持。无需 Visual Studio，无需 Rider 许可证，无供应商锁定。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="window">
    <div class="window-bar">
      <div class="window-controls" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="window-dot window-dot-red"></span>
        <span class="window-dot window-dot-yellow"></span>
        <span class="window-dot window-dot-green"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="window-title">Program.cs — Forge</div>
      <div class="window-tools" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">play_arrow</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bug_report</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-pane"><code><span class="token-keyword">using</span> System;
<span class="token-keyword">using</span> System.Diagnostics;

<span class="token-keyword">namespace</span> Forge.Demo
{
    <span class="token-keyword">public class</span> Program
    {
        <span class="token-keyword">public static void</span> Main()
        {
            <span class="token-type">var</span> sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();

            Console.WriteLine(<span class="token-string">"Initializing Forge workspace..."</span>);

            <span class="token-type">var</span> parser = <span class="token-keyword">new</span> FastSyntaxParser();
            parser.AnalyzeProject();

            sw.Stop();
            Console.WriteLine(<span class="token-string">$"Ready in {sw.ElapsedMilliseconds}ms"</span>);
        }
    }
}</code></pre>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="panel">
  <div class="card-grid card-grid-three">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">explore</span>
      <h2>完整语言智能</h2>
      <p>Roslyn 驱动的 C# 和 FCS 驱动的 F# 代码补全、悬停提示、跳转到定义、查找引用和重命名——与编译器精度一致。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">view_in_ar</span>
      <h2>NuGet 集成</h2>
      <p>无需离开编辑器即可浏览、安装和更新 NuGet 包，通过标准 LSP 命令在所有支持的编辑器中可用。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">analytics</span>
      <h2>内置性能分析器</h2>
      <p>内存分配追踪和 CPU 性能分析直接集成到编辑器工作流中，无需切换到独立工具。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">code_blocks</span>
      <h2>F# 一等公民</h2>
      <p>通过专用的 FSharp.Compiler.Service sidecar 提供完整 F# 支持，不是附加功能，F# 特性有独立的验收标准和测试覆盖。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">build</span>
      <h2>重构与代码操作</h2>
      <p>Roslyn 驱动的代码操作：提取方法、重命名、整理导入、批量修复建议——与闭源替代品同等质量。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-box" aria-hidden="true">search</span>
      <h2>解决方案资源管理器</h2>
      <p>在编辑器内浏览完整的 .sln 或 .slnx 解决方案树、管理项目并深入查看依赖关系。</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

